ficient.","test_description":"Instantiate the real ApprovalWorkflow, set a draft, request approval but do not grant it, attempt to send, and verify a blocking error is raised. Then approve and verify sending succeeds. Use real workflow objects to catch control-flow bugs, but mock the email send API.","plan_consistent":true,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.3,"Integration":0.55,"System":0.1,"Agentic":0.02,"Workflow":0.03}},{"behavior_id":5,"description":"The full sequence — read thread, generate draft, check facts, present for approval — works end-to-end for a real email thread.","minimum_level":"Workflow","justification":"This behavior spans multiple agentic steps in sequence (draft generation and fact checking both depend on real LLM outputs). The failure could be in integration between steps (e.g., the draft format breaks the fact checker, or the fact checker output is not presented correctly), not in individual steps. Mocking the LLMs at intermediate steps would hide failures in how their outputs are passed and consumed downstream. Testing with real LLM calls for both generation and checking is needed.","test_description":"Run the full pipeline with a real email thread: (1) read and parse the thread, (2) call the real LLM draft generator, (3) run the real fact checker on the draft, (4) present the result for approval. Verify that all steps complete without data format errors, each step's output is compatible with the next step's input, and the approval UI receives all necessary information. Use real LLM calls for generation and fact-checking.","plan_consistent":true,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.02,"Integration":0.08,"System":0.05,"Agentic":0.15,"Workflow":0.7}}]},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13710,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13710},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"